  m_text: '

    Dev Log Version 1.0.2


    The Environtment Update:


    Updated
    the Planet Sprites.


    Added Solar Systems that move, that spawn around the
    world.


    Added Environmental lighting to the game.


    Added Bloom to lights.


    Added
    Asteroids that spawn every 5 minutes.


    Tweeked that xp cost per level to
    be less for easier leveling.'
