      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Dev Log Version 1.0.1a\n\nAdded new skill Backward fire where it shoots
    an extra bullet behind the player.\n\nAdded a setting to swap the players ship
    sprite. \n\nWorked on the enemy AI to hopefully be a little smarter with its
    predictive movements\n\nMade the Enemies clump together when the player is too
    far away.\n\nAdded the Dev Logs (Which werent here before just added Version
    1.0 so you could know what was added then).\n\nMade Double Shot work for all
    weapons instead of just minigun and missile.\n "
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
