  m_text: "Dev Log Version 1.2\n\nBosses and new sprites\n\r\nWhat's new \r\n\r\n[A
    New Sprite] This update brings a new sprite for the player (currently only the
    one) with a different gun sprite for each weapon.\r\n\r\n[All Enemy Types Out]
    This update fixes any bug that and makes it so all enemy types can spawn so now
    it's more than just fighting the missiles.\r\n\r\n[Bosses] The update brings
    3 test bosses to the game which are subject to change.\n"
